channel.title: Someone help! I'm so CONFUSED!
channel.description:
I don't get it! I don't know how to start playing. I dunno how to start at all... I pick and IP from the IP list, then put it in file>new server. Then I put in the right port at file>new port. Then I put the IP again in file>ping server.
Then I put my ID and pass and the IP thing, but it still says it can't connect!
What the heck am I doing wrong?
Someone help ._. this is my first time trying to play on a private server on ANY game and I thought this would be a good place to start, but it's so complicated!
